result.name: Bahce Turkish Restaurant

reviews.text:
Awsome food. The service was also great. We ordered a mango lassi and then my friend was not comfortable with the smell. They immediately replaced it with a drink of her choice without any extra charge.

Its good on the pocket. The sheesh kebab platter is a must try
Famous lamb kebabs and other Turkish style food.  We enjoyed consistent great quality over the last 6 years.  Also conveniently  close to the Mui Wo ferry terminal.
Service extremely slow, nearly an hour wait for a fish wrap. It wasn't worth the wait either.
Friendly Service. Food was good. Pity they had run out of the Calamari.
its a great place the food is amazing best turkish restaurant I have visited 😍
